msgstr "<strong>ໃຊ້ປະໂຫຍດຈາກຄຸນສົມບັດການຈັບຄູ່:</strong>"

#. module: real_estate
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:real_estate.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Offer and digital signature</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ຂໍ້ສະເໜີ ແລະ ການເຊັນຊື່ດິຈິຕອນ</strong>"

#. module: real_estate
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:real_estate.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Optimize your CRM:</strong> Add automated emails and template "
